<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أخذ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(مَا مِنْ دَابَّةٍ إِلاَّ هُوَ آخِذٌ بِنَاصِيَتِهَا)</span> <span style="color:#950000">" ٥٦/ هود "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
